about.description:
A setup is to the PAW method what a pseudo-potential is to the
pseudo-potential method.

name: gpaw-data
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "gpaw-data" %}
{% set version = "0.9.20000" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://wiki.fysik.dtu.dk/gpaw-files/gpaw-setups-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6c71682be12a41e17909f65fd7c1a2e4a6a7becb63fbeed2f0f3a1616d6fd41f

build:
  noarch: generic
  number: 2
  run_exports:
    - {{ pin_subpackage('gpaw-data', max_pin='x.x.x') }}

requirements:
  build:
  run:
